7 December 2013Minister in The Presidency for Performance, Monitoring and Evaluation as well as Administration Collins Chabane will today brief the media on developments of the state funeral of former President Nelson Mandela. Details of the briefing are as follows: Date: 07 December 2013 Time: 13h00 Venue: SABC studios, Auckland Park Government has also created a dedicated website where all announcements and media related information is uploaded daily: www.mandela.gov.za. Enquiries: Phumla Williams, Acting Government Spokesperson 083 501 0139 or Mr Harold Maloka 082 847 9799 Issued by Government Communication and Information System